{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "丁鹏携阿古、小香闯入连云山庄，救出被掳的妻子青青和侍女小云。阿古一脚踢倒大门，阴阳怪气的两名寺人率先冲出欲攻击小香，被阿古反手提起互撞而死。丁鹏随后以圆月弯刀连破三批拦截，六名煞星被一刀劈成十二片，第三批八人中五人逃散，阿古追杀殆尽。丁鹏救出青青后，两人就贞操与牺牲展开深入对话，彼此在观念上有了新的理解。与此同时，玉无瑕在地下秘室中清点连云十四煞星的全部银票和账簿，随后点燃浸油棉线引燃整个连云山庄，带着所有钱财从地道离开。她在山庄外遇见尾随而来的柳若松，两人一番唇枪舌剑。正当玉无瑕以袖中软剑偷袭柳若松未果时，昔年魔教长老金狮和银龙应信香召见赶来。玉无瑕交代二人教训柳若松后飘然离去，并提及曾开罪铁燕双飞之事。银龙透露铁燕双飞已被处置。柳若松认出金狮银龙身份后惊恐万分。章末交代了魔教昔年与五大门派在祁连山决战、教主坠崖、铜驼背负少主逃亡的往事背景。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "老马，你回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "是……是的，回来了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "老秦呢？怎么没一起回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "他被丁鹏一刀劈成两片，那实在是一柄可怕的刀。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "他若劈了一个还算客气的，大概是要你领他前来，才没有劈掉你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "丁鹏呢？他是否杀了柳若松？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "没……没有，他看了字条后，拔出了刀，我们以为他要杀柳若松了，谁知道他竟把老秦劈了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "你们没有把话说清楚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "不！不！说得很清楚，一句话没少说。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "那就是说，他宁可牺牲他的老婆，也不愿意杀掉柳若松。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "不！他也没有这么说。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "他究竟怎么说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "他说他不会砍人的头，只会把人劈成两片，叫我们下次要他杀人的时候，要换个方式。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "他只说了这一句？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "他还说了很多，总而言之归纳起来只有一句话，他不会受我们的威胁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "用他老婆也不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "用他老婆也不行，他说我们可以杀死他的妻子，但是要付出很大的代价。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "然后他就放你回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "你真是笨蛋，难道你不知道这是他的诡计，要你带路，好跟着你回来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "我当然想到了，一路上特别注意，而且通知了十七个暗哨，要他们注意我的身后，结果证明他并没有跟踪前来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_lao_ma",
      "text": "哦！这倒是令人百思难解了，难道他对他的老婆一点都不关心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "老马",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "也不是，他说他自然有办法找到他的妻子，他们之间心有灵犀可通，哪怕是远在千里之外都能很快地找到她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "活见他妈的大头鬼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出去，尽一切的力量，格杀来人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连云十四煞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_sha_member",
      "speaker_name": "六煞之一",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是丁鹏，是你们捉住了我的妻子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_sha_member",
      "speaker_name": "六煞之一",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸡犬不留。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁郎，还有什么好笑的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我只是为你们的傻而感到好笑，那个玉无瑕只脱掉了你们的衣服，就把你们困在这楼上了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，要我那种样子在别的男人面前出现，我宁可死了的好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "难道你没有听过事急从权？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不可以，这是一个女人的贞操。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你知道我绝不会在那种情形下认为你不贞的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道，但是我却自己有不贞的感觉。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这种感觉是那么重要吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，非常重要。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "有没有哪种力量能改变你这种感觉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有，在一个情形下，我可以不顾一切。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "什么情形？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你在危险的时候，而我那么做可以使你脱险，即使是要我献身给另一个男人，我也会那么做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "青青，与其要你那么做，我还是宁可死了的好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "幸好我那样做的机会太少了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "是因为我已经没有危险的可能了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不！你的武功越高，危险也越多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "既然我的危险多，为什么你那么做的可能很少呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为能使你陷人险境的，一定是非常厉害的圈套，更是人家苦心设计的圈套，他们的目的是杀死你，而不是得到我，因此，即使我想献出自己来解救你，也是不可能的事，所以我才说不可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "不！青青，你错了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "是的，不但错了，而且错得厉害，我现在对我自己的状况很了解，也许有圈套能使我陷入险境，但是绝不可能杀死我，不过你若是认为我已经陷入险境而那样做了，才真正地要我命了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你会因而杀了自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "不会，我只担心你自己不想活下去，而失去了你，才是我真正不想活的时候。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不！丁郎，你也错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我也错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，假如我真为了救你而失身给另一个男人，我绝不会有不贞的感觉，更不会因而轻生，反而会活得更有意思，更有乐趣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "更有乐趣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，因为我发现自己对你还有更大的用处，作更多的贡献，自己活得更起劲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "说得对，我是错了，你错了一次，我也错了一次，我们扯平了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的，丁郎，扯平了，我们以为对彼此已很了解了，哪知道在观念上还有着如此大的错误。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "小云",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "爷，玉无瑕呢？那个臭婆娘呢？你有没有杀了她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再见，连云山庄，再见，连云十四煞星，再见，玉无瑕。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "谢谢你，丁鹏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "是你，柳若松？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "是我，柳若松。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "你怎么来了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "你要我的脑袋，我又怎能不来？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "那只是一个无伤大雅的玩笑，你自己也明白，丁鹏不会杀你的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "我在他心目中的地位还没有你想像中那么重要。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 615
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "柳若松，你未免把自己看得太轻了，他不是因为你很重要而不杀你，而是因为你微不足道而不杀你，正如一条死狗躺在路上，你叫任何一个路人去踢他一脚，很少会有人肯答应的，因为人怕踢脏了自己的脚。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "你居然敢对我说这种话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "为什么不敢说，这原本是事实，在我，在任何一个人看来，你就是这样一个人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "很不幸的，你却被一条躺在路上的死狗咬住了小辫子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "你以为抓住我的把柄了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "难道你还不承认？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "我当然可以不承认，因为你在一般人的心目中的分量，你自己明白，别人放个屁也比你说的话香，有人会相信吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 639,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "那你不妨试试看，柳某说的话或许比屁还臭，但是只要柳某把这件事传出去，总会有人听到的，哪怕是当作笑话来听，多少对你也有点妨碍的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "柳若松不是好人，不是君子，而且是个很多疑的小人，所以柳某不容易受到人家的暗算。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 659,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "柳某的武功在丁鹏的刀下，固然不值得一顾，但是在一般江湖上，多少也可以算个高手，虽不一定能胜过你，但是你想杀死我还不容易。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "我又何必要杀你，杀你又何必要我亲自动手？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 671,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "我知道你可以策动一批裙下之臣来对付我，但是他们的分量够得上吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "柳若松，你未免太看得起自己了，我不必动用家里的人手，随便招招手找一个来，也够你消受的了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 679,
      "line_end": 679
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "柳某不是灯草扎的，不会被一阵大风吹倒的，在当今江湖上，除了丁鹏之外，柳某还没有把别人放在心上。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 683,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruosong",
      "text": "我不想吓唬你，只不过我也不想骗你，从现在起，我向前走七步，走到第七步上，你最好就把在这儿看见我的事情忘记掉，否则你就会后悔了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "两位老伯好，好久不见了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 733,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi",
      "speaker_name": "金狮",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "姑娘好，蒙以信香召见，不知有何要我们效劳的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 735,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "老伯太客气了，靶女只是有点小麻烦，发动信香，只想随便请个人来帮忙的，哪知竟把二位老伯惊动了，靶女十分过意不去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 739,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_long",
      "speaker_name": "银龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "我们恰好在附近，接获信香，以为姑娘遇上了大麻烦了呢，所以才联袂赶来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "其实也不算什么，只不过这个姓柳的家伙突然摸了来，而且他似乎比我想像中还要高明一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 747,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi",
      "speaker_name": "金狮",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "这太容易了，交给我们好了，姑娘要他怎么样？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 751
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "这家伙虽然讨厌，但留着总比死掉的好，只是他对如何活下去，还不太明白，请二位开导他一下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 757,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_long",
      "speaker_name": "银龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "姑娘放心好了，老朽们会办妥的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 761,
      "line_end": 761
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "有二位老伯出来，靶女没什么不放心了，靶女要快点赶回去，就不再多打扰二位老伯了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 763,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "对了，有件事靶女还想麻烦二位老伯一下，上次我确是不知道，才开罪了铁燕双飞老两口儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 769,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi",
      "speaker_name": "金狮",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "姑娘放心，那一次是老朽们疏忽，叫姑娘受了惊，幸喜姑娘无恙，以后他们绝不敢来找麻烦了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 773,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "玉无瑕",
      "listener": "char_jin_shi",
      "text": "对他们说我很抱歉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 777
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_long",
      "speaker_name": "银龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu_xia",
      "text": "无须麻烦了，对于两个断了手的人，我们实在懒得老跟他们哕嗦，而且心怀仇念的人也容易误事，所以我们已经叫他们到一个地方去休息了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 779,
      "line_end": 780
    }
  ],
